channel.title: Server Status Page Help
channel.description:
Everytime I try to register my server I get this message
Welcome staticfish1! The server Runestrike508 is offline, it must be online before you can register it here.
It is online because me, and 3 of my friends are on. The No-ip DUC settings are:
(No-IP Address) (open smiley face) Run on start up checked On the connection tab of my no-ip both overrides are checked When I click ok again it becomes a smiley face with red cheeks.
Please Post Your No-ip DUC settings [br][br][size=1]Posted on: November 08, 2009, 03:47:34 pm[/size][hr]Are you guys kidding me? 18 people have read this topic and no one has posted! You probably all use No-ip! How hard can it be to open it up and click the options button, connection, and tell me what is there![br][br][size=1]Posted on: November 08, 2009, 04:23:52 pm[/size][hr]PLEASE
